cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.CE, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) techniques to extract information from clinical notes, which falls under the scope of this category.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes an ensemble model using vector space modeling and topic modeling, which are machine learning techniques.
- cs.CY (Computers and Society): The paper discusses the use of electronic health records (EHRs) and their impact on healthcare, which is a societal issue related to the use of technology.
- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science): The paper applies computational techniques to healthcare data, which can be considered as a form of computational science.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses deep learning techniques and proposes an ensemble model to predict readmission, which falls under the scope of AI.
